---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <Image
      width="150"
      height="150"
      src="/sticker.png"
      class="w-auto max-h-[150px] select-none absolute right-[-110px] bottom-[-20px] z-[-1] opacity-50 md:opacity-100 md:relative md:right-auto md:bottom-auto md:z-auto pointer-events-none"
      alt="facts"
    />
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      My primary tools of choice includes:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>Go</li>
        <li>Rust</li>
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>TypeScript</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
        <Image
      width="150"
      height="150"
      src="/hiking.png"
      class="w-auto max-h-[150px] select-none absolute right-[-110px] bottom-[-20px] z-[-1] opacity-50 md:opacity-100 md:relative md:right-auto md:bottom-auto md:z-auto pointer-events-none"
      alt="hiking"
    />
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about fishing, golfing, or anything that gets my in nature.
      A peculiar hobby of mine is to bird watch or sit and listen to birds while reading a book.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
